      "author": "MsquareAutomation (Msquare Automation Solutions)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Automate Your Workflows with Monday and Toggl Track! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/clock3.png?v=12\" title=\":clock3:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":clock3:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Exciting news, automators! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bulb.png?v=12\" title=\":bulb:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bulb:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> We’ve just set up three powerful scenarios in <a href=\"http://Make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a> using Monday and Toggl Track that will supercharge your productivity! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Scenario 1: Client Sync Magic <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/sparkles.png?v=12\" title=\":sparkles:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":sparkles:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></strong><br />\nEvery time a new item is born in our Monday board, our <a href=\"http://Make.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Make.com</a> flow kicks in, listing clients in Toggl Track. And if the client doesn’t exist, bam! We create it on the fly in Toggl Track. No more manual entries, just pure automation awesomeness! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/arrows_counterclockwise.png?v=12\" title=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/clipboard.png?v=12\" title=\":clipboard:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":clipboard:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Scenario 2:Automated Project Creation <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></strong><br />\nHere’s where things get interesting. When a subitem’s toggle checkbox is checked in Monday, we automatically fetch that item and create a corresponding project in Toggl Track. Seamless project creation without missing a beat!</p>\n<p><strong>Scenario 3: Time Entry Mastery <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/alarm_clock.png?v=12\" title=\":alarm_clock:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":alarm_clock:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></strong><br />\nUpdating time entries in Toggl Track and grabbing detailed reports is a breeze. We dive deep into projects and clients, seamlessly linking Monday subitems with Toggl Track clients. <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/bar_chart.png?v=12\" title=\":bar_chart:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":bar_chart:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/arrows_counterclockwise.png?v=12\" title=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":arrows_counterclockwise:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Say goodbye to manual cross-referencing headaches! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/no_entry_sign.png?v=12\" title=\":no_entry_sign:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":no_entry_sign:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/massage_man.png?v=12\" title=\":massage_man:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":massage_man:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Scenario 3: True Value, True Project <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/star2.png?v=12\" title=\":star2:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":star2:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><br />\nToggle that value in Toggl Track, and watch the magic unfold! <a href=\"http://xn--Make-zn4b37750a.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">🎉✨Make.com</a>  triggers a party, creating a brand new project in Toggl Track. Who said automation couldn’t be fun? <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/confetti_ball.png?v=12\" title=\":confetti_ball:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":confetti_ball:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/computer.png?v=12\" title=\":computer:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":computer:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Why You’ll Love It:<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Efficiency: No more tedious data entry.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Accuracy: Keep your data synced and error-free.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Real-time Updates: Stay on top of your game, always.<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=12\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Streamlined Workflow: Connect your Monday and Toggl Track like never before!</p>\n<p>Ready to transform your work life? <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/rocket.png?v=12\" title=\":rocket:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":rocket:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> Try it out today and let the automation revolution begin! <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/globe_with_meridians.png?v=12\" title=\":globe_with_meridians:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":globe_with_meridians:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/briefcase.png?v=12\" title=\":briefcase:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":briefcase:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p><span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#AutomationNation</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#MondayMagic</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#TogglTrackTales</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#MakeAdventures</span> <span class=\"hashtag-raw\">#ProductivityBoost</span></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/9/09f11ce3d61f3302afb3d393154d0daff8d26c36.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/9/09f11ce3d61f3302afb3d393154d0daff8d26c36_2_689x323.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"689\" height=\"323\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1290×604 51 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/b/8/b8d5d0894caec32f8c94b3486cc4a9475a3d9bcc.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/b/8/b8d5d0894caec32f8c94b3486cc4a9475a3d9bcc_2_690x325.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"325\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1284×606 46.7 KB</span></div></a></div><br />\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/c/2cfeaf454a493ab9667b6cd352d0f27a7898c76d.png\" title=\"image\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/c/2cfeaf454a493ab9667b6cd352d0f27a7898c76d_2_690x325.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"690\" height=\"325\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">1271×599 55.6 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>If you are new to Make, here is our magic link to get 1 Month Pro plan free (10,000 operations):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare\" class=\"onebox\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=msquare</a></p>\n<p>If you need any implementation support kindly contact us</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://calendly.com/msquarepro/meeting\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">MSquare Support</a><br />\nVi